            <h3>Browse Products</h3>
            <p>View HubSpot products used for bookings.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-lightgrey" href="/hubspot/products">Browse products</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr/>
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Create Course Booking</strong>: generates Forecast project, delivery/admin tasks, and a Google Calendar event.</li>
        <li><strong>Create Tasks (Import)</strong>: upload tasks for existing Forecast projects.</li>
        <li><strong>Browse</strong>: explore Products (HubSpot), Projects and Labels (Forecast), and Bookings.</li>
    </ol>
</section>
